    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="text-white">
  <div id="particles-js" class="bg-gray-900 w-full h-full"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="py-2">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">
        <a href="/"><i class="fas fa-bolt text-yellow-500"></i> flasheet</a>
      </h1>
    </nav>

    <header class="text-center py-6">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight">
        Instantly turn your <span class="text-green-300">Google Sheet</span>
        <br /><span class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl">into an API.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="lg:text-xl py-4 text-gray-200">
        Launch your application, website, or whatever at the speed of light!
      </p>
      <div class="pt-10 pb-6">
        <a class="btn py-4 bg-yellow-400 text-gray-900 hover:bg-yellow-300" href="/auth/google"><i
            class="fab fa-google"></i> Sign In with Google</a>
      </div>
